{"tid":747513,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港|社會階層】力爭上游 OR 安份守己？","createTime":"2018-07-18T12:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T17:34:26.000Z","uid":180390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8abecb830b2047b59198ce7fb4e56607f171ef10","tid":747513,"uid":180390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"最近睇套劇，有提到古代貴族同奴隸嘅野⋯<br />\n<br />\n跟住唸，社會階層真係無分國界、時間咁存在。無論係古今中外，社會階層都有係到。當然大家都知，奴隸制度已經廢除左。<br />\n<br />\n但係，依家社會階層依然存在 e.g 中層、基層～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">究竟，作為一個人，要力爭向上流或是安份守己呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亂畫左個香港階層金字塔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/200732_6f1c14583634bbbcd72ec404a19b77ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F200732_6f1c14583634bbbcd72ec404a19b77ef.png&h=db90d68a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccbfeb2b2dce1f78882e8ff0c714d1e6f13c09ea","tid":747513,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"係唔係應該分返開租同買?"},{"pid":"c1b1b64fe6cfb641e3afb6e76502bdb4ada4f0c0","tid":747513,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:30:08.000Z","msg":"究竟，作為一個人，要力爭向上流或是安份守己呢？<br />\n<br />\n依個先係問題，對上嗰d係廢話，下面嗰d係有用資訊。"},{"pid":"82ada5582c778706e4b7ac62c945a3ab33084a37","tid":747513,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:34:26.000Z","msg":"冇得揀力爭下流?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}